---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Office Furniture Installation DC, Northern Virginia & Maryland | My Furniture Installer"
  description="Professional office furniture installation, cubicle reconfiguration, and office layout redesign in Washington DC, Northern Virginia, and Maryland. Free consultations."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Service Areas</h1>
      <p>Professional office furniture installation and reconfiguration services throughout the greater Washington DC metropolitan area.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2>Local Expertise, Regional Reach</h2>
        <p>Based in the DC metro area, we provide expert office furniture installation and reconfiguration services to businesses throughout Washington DC, Northern Virginia, and Maryland. Our local presence means faster response times, lower transportation costs, and installers who know the area.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section location-section" id="dc">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="location-content">
        <div class="location-text">
          <span class="location-badge">Washington DC</span>
          <h2>Office Furniture Installation in Washington DC</h2>
          <p>From Capitol Hill to Georgetown, we serve businesses across the nation's capital with professional office furniture installation and reconfiguration services. Whether you're a government contractor, law firm, nonprofit, or tech company, we help DC businesses optimize their workspace.</p>
          <h3>DC Office Furniture Services</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Office furniture installation DC</li>
            <li>Cubicle reconfiguration and layout planning</li>
            <li>Workstation assembly and installation</li>
            <li>Office moves and furniture relocation</li>
            <li>Systems furniture breakdown and reinstallation</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>DC Neighborhoods We Serve</h3>
          <div class="area-tags">
            <span>Downtown DC</span>
            <span>Capitol Hill</span>
            <span>Georgetown</span>
            <span>Navy Yard</span>
            <span>Dupont Circle</span>
            <span>Foggy Bottom</span>
            <span>Penn Quarter</span>
            <span>NoMa</span>
            <span>K Street</span>
            <span>McPherson Square</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="location-visual">
          <div class="visual-card dc">
            <div class="visual-icon">&#127963;</div>
            <div class="visual-stat">
              <span class="stat-value">500+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">DC projects completed</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section location-section alt" id="virginia">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="location-content reverse">
        <div class="location-text">
          <span class="location-badge">Northern Virginia</span>
          <h2>Cubicle Reconfiguration in Northern Virginia</h2>
          <p>Northern Virginia's dynamic business environment demands flexible office spaces. From Arlington's corporate towers to Tysons' tech hubs, we help Virginia businesses reconfigure their existing furniture to adapt to changing needs while saving significant costs.</p>
          <h3>Northern Virginia Office Services</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Cubicle reconfiguration Northern Virginia</li>
            <li>Office furniture installation and assembly</li>
            <li>Open office layout design and implementation</li>
            <li>Panel system installation and reconfiguration</li>
            <li>Furniture asset inventory and assessment</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Virginia Areas We Serve</h3>
          <div class="area-tags">
            <span>Arlington</span>
            <span>Tysons</span>
            <span>McLean</span>
            <span>Fairfax</span>
            <span>Alexandria</span>
            <span>Reston</span>
            <span>Herndon</span>
            <span>Vienna</span>
            <span>Falls Church</span>
            <span>Chantilly</span>
            <span>Sterling</span>
            <span>Ashburn</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="location-visual">
          <div class="visual-card virginia">
            <div class="visual-icon">&#127961;</div>
            <div class="visual-stat">
              <span class="stat-value">50-60%</span>
              <span class="stat-label">average cost savings</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section location-section" id="maryland">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="location-content">
        <div class="location-text">
          <span class="location-badge">Maryland</span>
          <h2>Office Layout Redesign in Maryland</h2>
          <p>From Bethesda's professional services firms to Silver Spring's diverse business community, we provide comprehensive office layout redesign services throughout Maryland. Our team helps Maryland businesses maximize their existing furniture investment.</p>
          <h3>Maryland Office Services</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Office layout redesign Maryland</li>
            <li>Cubicle installation and reconfiguration</li>
            <li>Modular furniture systems installation</li>
            <li>Office space planning and optimization</li>
            <li>Furniture breakdown and relocation</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Maryland Areas We Serve</h3>
          <div class="area-tags">
            <span>Bethesda</span>
            <span>Silver Spring</span>
            <span>Rockville</span>
            <span>Gaithersburg</span>
            <span>College Park</span>
            <span>Chevy Chase</span>
            <span>Greenbelt</span>
            <span>Bowie</span>
            <span>Lanham</span>
            <span>Laurel</span>
            <span>Columbia</span>
            <span>Annapolis</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="location-visual">
          <div class="visual-card maryland">
            <div class="visual-icon">&#127970;</div>
            <div class="visual-stat">
              <span class="stat-value">5-10</span>
              <span class="stat-label">day project turnaround</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section why-local">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Choose a Local Provider?</h2>
        <p>Working with a DC-area company has real advantages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128205;</div>
          <h3>Same-Day Response</h3>
          <p>We can visit your site quickly for assessments, emergency service, or project follow-ups.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128666;</div>
          <h3>Lower Costs</h3>
          <p>Local operations mean reduced transportation and logistics costs that we pass on to you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128101;</div>
          <h3>Area Knowledge</h3>
          <p>We understand DC-area building requirements, parking logistics, and local business needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128170;</div>
          <h3>Reliable Support</h3>
          <p>Post-project support is always nearby. Need an adjustment? We'll be there.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    title="Get a Free Consultation in Your Area"
    description="Contact us for a no-obligation site visit and reconfiguration plan. We'll show you how much you can save."
    buttonText="Get Your Free Plan"
    buttonHref="/contact"
  />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: calc(var(--header-height) + 4rem) 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg-light) 0%, var(--color-bg) 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .intro-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .intro-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .intro-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .location-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .location-section.alt {
    background: var(--color-bg-light);
  }

  .location-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .location-content.reverse {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
  }

  .location-content.reverse .location-text {
    order: 2;
  }

  .location-content.reverse .location-visual {
    order: 1;
  }

  .location-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .location-text h2 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .location-text > p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .location-text h3 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-list {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-list li {
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding: 0.375rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-list li::before {
    content: '\\2713';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-success);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .area-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .area-tags span {
    padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .location-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .visual-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg-alt) 0%, var(--color-bg-light) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 220px;
  }

  .visual-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .visual-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .visual-stat .stat-value {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .visual-stat .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .why-local {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .location-content,
    .location-content.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .location-content.reverse .location-text,
    .location-content.reverse .location-visual {
      order: unset;
    }

    .location-visual {
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
